"title": "5407: merchants",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5407",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Traders who bought and sold goods and articles of value, often transporting their wares from one country to another according to the demands in different localities.</p>\n<h2>Some merchants transported their goods by caravan</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:25-Gen37:28\">GEN 37:25–37:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:15-Job6:21\">JOB 6:15–6:21</a></p>\n<h2>Some merchants traded by sea</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:14\">PRO 31:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:26-1Kgs9:28\">1KI 9:26–9:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:17-2Chr8:18\">2CH 8:17–8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:11-1Kgs10:12\">1KI 10:11–10:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:10-2Chr9:11\">2CH 9:10–9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:48\">1KI 22:48</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:35-2Chr20:37\">2CH 20:35–20:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:23\">PSA 107:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:2-Isa23:3\">ISA 23:2–23:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:25\">EZK 27:25</a></p>\n<h2>Merchants often lived close to one another</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:11\">ZEP 1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:31-Neh3:32\">NEH 3:31–3:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:4\">EZK 17:4</a></p>\n<h2>Merchants set the standards for weights and measures</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:16\">GEN 23:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:7\">HOS 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:4-Amos8:6\">AMO 8:4–8:6</a></p>\n<h2>Ordinary citizens sold goods to merchants</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:24\">PRO 31:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:28\">GEN 37:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:18-Prov31:19\">PRO 31:18–31:19</a></p>\n<h2>Merchants were credited with wisdom and shrewdness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:44-Matt13:46\">MAT 13:44–13:46</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Goods traded by merchants</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:11-Rev18:13\">REV 18:11–18:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song3:6\">SNG 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:12-Ezek27:24\">EZK 27:12–27:24</a></p>\n<h2>Merchants flourished during Solomon's reign</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:14-1Kgs10:15\">1KI 10:14–10:15</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:13-2Chr9:14\">2CH 9:13–9:14</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:21-1Kgs10:22\">1KI 10:21–10:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:20-2Chr9:21\">2CH 9:20–9:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:26-1Kgs10:29\">1KI 10:26–10:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:14-2Chr1:17\">2CH 1:14–1:17</a></p>\n<h2>Foreign merchants in Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:15-Neh13:22\">NEH 13:15–13:22</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Cities famed for their merchants</h2>\n<h3>Tyre</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:1-Ezek27:36\">EZK 27:1–27:36</a></p>\n<h3>Tarshish</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:13\">EZK 38:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:3\">JON 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Babylon the Great</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:2-Rev18:24\">REV 18:2–18:24</a></p>",
